title: #92Noon! Friday Football Feast from Eagan!
description: The FAN's Paul Allen and Paul Charchian are live from Buffalo Wild Wings in Eagan for the final feast of the regular season! Looking at the remains of it through a fantasy lens with Charch. Chad Greenway calls in from sunny California. Lavelle E. Neal III & former Viking, Eddie MacDaniel join the feast.
